zh_CN.DialogText: 望了望空空的背包，又回头看到了男人满面的愁容。

en_US.DialogText: Looking at the empty backpack, I looked back and saw the man's sad face.

zh_CN.DialogText: 嗯，我没办法一个人帮你。

en_US.DialogText: Well, I can't help you alone.

zh_CN.DialogText: 除了来找你之外，我已经想不出其他选择了。

en_US.DialogText: I can't think of any other choice but to come to you.

zh_CN.DialogText: 所以我们一起去找其他人来一起帮忙吧。

en_US.DialogText: So let's find someone else to help.

zh_CN.DialogText: 如果你觉得这是个好的解决方法的话....好吧

en_US.DialogText: If you think this is a good solution ..... ok
